  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. Boil the potatoes until tender, then let cool.",
    "3. Scoop out the centers of the potatoes and set aside.",
    "4. In a bowl, mix together the chicken, avocado, cilantro, scallions, sour cream, lime juice, salt, and pepper.",
    "5. Stuff each potato with the chicken mixture.",
    "6. Top each stuffed potato with a spoonful of salsa criolla.",
    "7. Bake the potatoes in the oven for 15-20 minutes, or until heated through."
